N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 §§ 1208-5.3 - Effective date

State Regulations

This Part shall take effect on January 1, 2015. Thereafter, the provisions of this Part shall supersede any and all inconsistent provisions
of Part 426. Notes
